<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Signaler un problème | ImmoFacile CI</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0B1120] text-white font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">

    <div class="w-full max-w-lg">
        <div class="mb-8">
            <a href="/dashboard-tenant" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                ← Retour à mon espace
            </a>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-4 text-red-500">Signaler un Incident</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400">Une panne ? Une fuite ? Dites-nous tout.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/report-issue" method="POST" class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-[2rem] space-y-6">
            
            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2">Titre du problème</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" required placeholder="Ex: Panne climatiseur chambre" 
                       class="w-full bg-[#0B1120] border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-red-500 transition">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2">Urgence</label>
                <select name="priority" class="w-full bg-[#0B1120] border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-red-500 transition">
                    <option value="LOW">Faible (Ça peut attendre)</option>
                    <option value="MEDIUM" selected>Moyenne (Gênant)</option>
                    <option value="HIGH">Haute (Urgent)</option>
                    <option value="URGENT">Critique (Danger / Inondation)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2">Détails</label>
                <textarea name="description" rows="4" required placeholder="Décrivez le problème..." 
                          class="w-full bg-[#0B1120] border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-red-500 transition"></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-black py-4 rounded-xl uppercase tracking-wider transition">
                Envoyer le signalement
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
